What you need to know:

Yussuf Poulsen gave the hosts a second-minute lead, but De Bruyne came off the bench at half-time to make his first appearance of the tournament after injury and teed up Thorgan Hazard to equalise before drilling in a fine strike.The match was paused after 10 minutes for a minute's applause for Eriksen, who suffered a cardiac arrest in the Danes' game against Finland last weekend.